<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Your Weekly Amenity Updates</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333;">
    <img src="https://crowded-airport.com/email.jpg" alt="Crowded Airport Header" style="width: 100%; height: auto;">
    <h1 style="color: #6366F1;">Hey {{name}}!</h1>

    <p>We’re excited to bring you this week’s updates for the amenities you've adopted at various airports. Here’s a look at how each one performed:</p>

    {{#each amenities}}
    <div style="background-color: #e6e6e6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin-top: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #6366F1; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 0;">Amenity Spotlight: {{this.thing.thing}} @ {{this.thing.airport.name}}</h2>
        {{#if this.navigationClicks.length}}
            <p><strong>Guided Adventures:</strong> A total of <strong>{{this.navigationClicks.length}}</strong> travelers navigated to your amenity this week. Great job in helping them find their way!</p>
        {{/if}}
        {{#if this.upvoteClicks.length}}
            <p><strong>Votes This Week:</strong> Received <strong>{{this.upvoteClicks.length}}</strong> votes, bringing the total score to <strong>{{this.thing.votes}}</strong>/5.</p>
        {{else}}
            <p><strong>Votes This Week:</strong> This amenity didn't receive any votes this week but is still going strong at <strong>{{this.thing.votes}}</strong>/5.</p>
        {{/if}}
    </div>
    {{/each}}

    <p>Wishing you a fantastic week ahead and safe travels wherever you are!</p>

    <p>Warm regards,</p>
    <strong>Rik Verbeek</strong><br><br>
    <strong>Crowded Airport</strong> – Where Your Contributions Make Journeys Brighter!
</body>
</html>
